<li class="commentbody highlighted" id="comment-333202">
			<cite><a href='http://smittenkitchen.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>deb</a></cite>
						&nbsp;
			<a class="commentlink" href="#comment-333202" title="">November 22, 2009</a> 

		
			<div class="commentcount">131</div>

				<p>It stays pretty moist. Room temperature, keep it covered.</p>
