<li class="commentbody" id="comment-602482">
			<cite>TaraM</cite>
						&nbsp;
			<a class="commentlink" href="#comment-602482" title="">March 20, 2011</a> 

		
			<div class="commentcount">221</div>

				<p>I made this cake for a friend&#8217;s St. Patrick&#8217;s Day party (which also involved a whole keg of guinness, and guinness stew). It came out really well, and everyone liked it.<br />
The only thing I would do differently next time is use less instant coffee powder in the chocolate. I used the Starbucks kind (Via Columbia) and maybe it&#8217;s stronger than regular instant coffee, because I thought the coffee flavor overpowered the chocolate. Not that it kept anyone from eating it, of course :)</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
<li class="commentbody" id="comment-608630">
